              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-506-79L1-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1">Who had been much abused in many different L<hi rend="small-caps">IBELS</hi>.</l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-506-79L1-headnote-2">
