          <head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-506-79L1-headnote-3">
            <lg n="1" xml:id="spp-506-79L1-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote">
              <l n="1" xml:id="spp-506-79L1-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"></l>
            </lg>
          </head>
          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-1" n="1"><hi rend="display-initial">T</hi>HE greatest Monarch may be stabb'd by night,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-2" n="2">And fortune help the murderer in his flight;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-3" n="3">The vilest ruffian may commit a rape,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-4" n="4">Yet safe from injur'd innocence escape;</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-5" n="5">And Calumny, by working under ground,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-6" n="6">Can, unreveng'd, the greatest merit wound.</l>
            <l rend="indent(1)" xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-7" n="7">WhatÂ·'s to be done? Shall Wit and Learning chuse</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-8" n="8">To live obscure, and have no fame to lose?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-9" n="9">By Censure frighted out of Honour's road,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-10" n="10">Nor dare to use the gifts by Heaven bestow'd?</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-11" n="11">Or fearless enter in through Virtue's gate,</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-506-79L1-line-12" n="12">And buy distinction at the dearest rate?</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
